				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "PAD players say when they reach mystra vault in Sorcerous Sundries basement. Depending on whether the karus book is being looked for in gale's quest and if players succeed on a passive check a different line will appear, giving or not a hint to how to leave the vault. The doors are each named after a famous wizard - Elminster, Ramazith, Silverhand and Karsus."
